-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Custom Scan (DocumentDBApiExplainQueryScan) (actual rows=4 loops=1)
   namespaceName: msdb.coll_ba
   indexName: b_1_a_1
   indexKey: {"b": 1,"a": 1}
   isMultiKey: false
   indexBounds: ["b": (MinKey, MaxKey), "a": [1, 1]], ["b": (MinKey, MaxKey), "a": [4, 4]]
   innerScanLoops: 5 loops
   scanType: ordered
   scanKeyDetails: key 1: [(isInequality: true, estimatedEntryCount: 4), (isInequality: true, estimatedEntryCount: 0)]
   ->  Index Scan using b_1_a_1 on documents_2214 collection (actual rows=4 loops=1)
         Index Cond: ((document @*= '{ "a" : [ { "$numberInt" : "1" }, { "$numberInt" : "4" } ] }'::bson) AND (document @<> '{ "b" : { "orderByScan" : { "$numberInt" : "1" } } }'::bson))
         Order By: (document |-<> '{ "b" : { "$numberInt" : "1" } }'::bson)
